```css
ul.menu-multilevel {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
}

ul.menu-multilevel > li {
    float: left;
    display: inline-block;
    position: relative;
    margin-right: 10px;
}

ul.menu-multilevel > li:hover ul {
    display: block;
    width: 200px;
}

ul.menu-multilevel ul {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
}

ul.menu-multilevel ul li {
    display: block;
}
```

